  "description": "A vibrant ruby-throated hummingbird perches on a thin, bare branch against a clear, bright blue sky. The hummingbird is facing slightly to the right, showcasing its iridescent green back and flanks, with a striking ruby-red throat patch. Its long, slender bill is prominent. The branch is brown and appears to be part of a deciduous tree, with small buds visible. The background is a uniform, cloudless blue, emphasizing the bird's colors.",
